## Quality Check Rules

**All quality verification is done locally. CI is for build confirmation only.**

### Flow

```
Change area detection (git diff)
    |
Static checks + tests
    |
Review cycles (persona + integrated review, minimum 3 cycles)
    |
E2E tests (final verification)
    |
Report data saved -> .quality-check-passed created -> push allowed
```

### Multi-Persona Review

4 specialist personas review in parallel as Agents:

| Persona | Focus Area |
|---------|-----------|
| Security Engineer | Vulnerabilities, auth, data leaks, injection |
| Software Architect | SOLID/DRY, layer responsibilities, dependencies, extensibility |
| QA Engineer | Edge cases, test coverage, error handling |
| Integration Architecture | Overall consistency, layer dependencies, existing patterns, side effects |

- **Completion criteria**: 0 must-fix items (Priority: High) from all 4 personas
- Minimum 3 cycles, repeat until 0 must-fix items

